<view class="container login-page">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="title">格物学术</view>
    <view class="muted gap-12">微信小程序版本</view>
    <view class="muted gap-12">点击下方按钮后将使用微信身份登录并创建平台账号。</view>

    <input
      class="input gap-24"
      placeholder="邀请码（可选）"
      value="{{ referrerCode }}"
      bindinput="onInputReferrer"
    />

    <button
      class="btn-primary gap-24"
      loading="{{ loading }}"
      disabled="{{ loading }}"
      bindtap="onTapWeChatLogin"
    >
      {{ loading ? "登录中..." : "微信一键登录" }}
    </button>

    <view class="muted gap-16">如遇问题，请先确认后台已开启“小程序登录”并配置 AppID/AppSecret。</view>
  </view>
</view>

